<title>Sang Muolpi Liem Mai Ta'n</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Guol lung tuok sam gibang khenna nuoi simlei ah,
 Lengin va bang na buol mahleng le;
 Sam gibang khenna din lenkawl ah ni a suok,
 Guol ngaih khenna'n thimthu, &quot;Dam takin&quot;
 Tih sawlang bang theilo.

[V2]
 Chang bang damin sang muolpi liem mai tan,
 Chung Pathien venna zal zo zelin;
 Lungtup na gam ninnuom I tun tieng,
 Lunglen thimthu khau bang sut lohna.
 Thangvan gam ninnuom ah;
 &quot;Dam takin&quot; tih sawlang bang tana.

[V3]
 2. Sietlei gamdai hi gibang kikhenna dinga,
 Zuo chung Pathien in tawngsie A lawh;
 Mahleh gibang khenlohna thangvan gam nuomah
 Nga banga I len tieng &quot;Dam takin,&quot;
 Tih sawlang bang tana.

[V4]
 3. Tuhin luonthi nulin gibang kikhen mah leng,
 Chung Pathien vanga chang bang damin;
 Dan leh gi bang kikhen lohna thangvan gamah,
 Luonthi nula sam gibang kikhen-
 Te tui bang kigawm ding.</lyrics>
</song>